{"tid":1333502,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[一定要推到1001] 爭取警隊脫離獨立薪級表","createTime":"2019-07-19T17:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T17:27:57.000Z","uid":171302,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3af7d862220d9d6d5aceb7c4546fe63ca3c6c03c","tid":1333502,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"【唔識唔緊要】議員教你睇《警隊條例》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《警隊條例》第8條，禁止警務人員參與職工會，但可以加入純由警務人員組成的組織。而第8條(4)指明警察4大工會職能，僅僅係為「福利及服務條件」提出意見，而唔係用嚟比你地政治表態用！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">事實上，警隊點解有獨立薪級表，《凌衞理報告書》第8.44段寫明係因為「法例禁止警察參加工會、禁止擅離職守及要求保持政治中立」。如今警隊多次借工會政治表態，係完全違反《警隊條例》，我將會同公務員事務局反映，要求警隊嚴格遵守政治中立，否則無需再依照《凌衞理報告書》俾警隊有獨立薪級表。</span><br />\n<br />\nbtw，員佐級協會主席向立法會主席投訴議員又係好幽默，請問你地搞清楚議會組成未？<br />\n<br />\n根據《基本法》第六十六至七十九條、《立法會行政管理委員會條例》（第443章）、《立法會(權力及特權)條例》（第382章）及《香港特別行政區立法會議事規則》（&quot;《議事規則》&quot;）訂明，立法會主席比一般議員多出嘅權力係「主持會議、維持會議秩序同行管會嘅行政角色」，根本無權處理發生係議會外嘅「投訴」。作為警察唔熟《警隊條例》都算，想寫信之前都讀多啲例先出聲啦。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 譚文豪Facebook <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n推到你班黑警人工同其他公務員睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好剝奪埋佢哋警察宿舍福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要萬四蚊起跳， 同ACO睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警入職人工:</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGy7m8m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGy7m8m.png&h=39ffbbc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1jBZU1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1jBZU1.png&h=461226ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEVmrEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEVmrEF.png&h=5ee1212d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一般公務員薪酬:</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZ9eMA5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZ9eMA5.png&h=d7746adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUB8QXA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUB8QXA.png&h=19ce19a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd4313e0975ef2ca37d9ae5342922e47673ef440","tid":1333502,"uid":171302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"一定要萬四蚊起跳， 同ACO睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b0d08a42b54ae598c5c3632740fe2241a12d3d","tid":1333502,"uid":171302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:18:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推到傳媒一齊討論研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c6dc83cddaf3386fe98f463cfb4c2f55766e3839","tid":1333502,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4313e0975ef2ca37d9ae5342922e47673ef440","tid":1333502,"uid":171302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"一定要萬四蚊起跳， 同ACO睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:23:00.000Z","msg":"ACO都要識下英文啦<br />\n黑警盲字都唔識多個 又冇紀律 邊值萬四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f2d194bb3b0d08243160021dd440291b6dfcfe","tid":1333502,"uid":171302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6dc83cddaf3386fe98f463cfb4c2f55766e3839","tid":1333502,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4313e0975ef2ca37d9ae5342922e47673ef440","tid":1333502,"uid":171302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"一定要萬四蚊起跳， 同ACO睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:23:00.000Z","msg":"ACO都要識下英文啦<br />